<figure style="max-width:1080px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 24px"><img src="/articles/automated-palletizing/1678303454-yaskawa-palletizing-cases-with-orange-filter.png" alt="Automated Palletizing: How It Works and How To Do It" style="width:100%;height:auto;display:block" /></figure>
